### Get all users - valid token
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken

###

### Get user by id
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken

###

### Create user
POST https://localhost:5001/api/users/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@techhive.com",
  "department": "HR"
}

###

### Update user
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/users/update/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "alice.smith@techhive.com",
  "department": "IT"
}

###

### Delete user
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/users/delete/1
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken

###

### Missing token
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users

###

### Invalid token
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users
Authorization: Bearer InvalidToken

###

### Trigger exception
GET https://localhost:5001/api/users/error
Authorization: Bearer TechHiveSecureToken